channel.title: Help, Moparscape will not work, and I'm pretty sure i have the newest Java
channel.description: I went to the java website and ran the test to check if I have latest version of Java. It said I do. But nither the Mopar web clent or download will work. If i try the web client it shows a white screen with an orange X in the upper right corner. Then if I try the downoad, it says that Mopoarscape has a problem geting to runescape and gives me some options that dont work... Here's a pic of the web client...[img][/img]
